Detailed Description

cvmx_npei_win_wr_data

NPEI_WIN_WR_DATA = NPEI Window Write Data Register

Contains the data to write to the address located in the NPEI_WIN_WR_ADDR Register. Writing the least-significant-byte of this register will cause a write operation to take place.
